{"tid":1398333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［繼續高汁］頭條新聞 17+2集 ： 眾叛親離","createTime":"2019-08-02T18:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T01:08:22.000Z","uid":31341,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"773cc9430fc8685540e2481a8633d0f325f2ff40","tid":1398333,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:22:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Y4untYS4Zr8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FY4untYS4Zr8&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDR%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=dd6dbf1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Y4untYS4Zr8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為太過高汁 我馬尿忍唔住<br />\n<br />\n由其最後果part 首讓子彈飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c698bb2692dc76d9a63acb5365c9c0d85ac710","tid":1398333,"uid":31341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:24:37.000Z","msg":"開火 為鎮守一個最微細盼望<br />\n無懼遠射炮像煙花放<br />\n為了家一個 這樣脆弱都抵抗<br />\n傷口 倦了的軀幹滲著了血汗<br />\n無論吃敗仗會極之沮喪<br />\n就算多沮喪 拼命拼命的反抗<br />\n園林埋下了炸藥亦要擋<br />\n憑靈魂能燃燒出一線光<br />\n孩童期望會笑著吃糖<br />\n開火 為你的家眷避免震盪<br />\n寧願去面對敵軍兇惡<br />\n面對子彈殼 結局要是多悲壯<br />\n軍隊 就算犧牲了繼續會盼望<br />\n期望戰地裡杜鵑開放<br />\n在遠方觀看 人間天清氣朗<br />\n這是不死的守望 要是一死都反抗"},{"pid":"88aff89367edce04d45f5ac12a333f68298dcd99","tid":1398333,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:26:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fbfc1352cea2e60e888d07a474e4e29e7cd4592","tid":1398333,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:39:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"979d2d98737de45de63ca0dafd2b94a0ceca8a05","tid":1398333,"uid":20776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:44:37.000Z","msg":"塞紅隧<br />\n塞鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e3546f4cba28ba468fc3b666ae0c2832ce6cd2","tid":1398333,"uid":54431,"like":